altTextOverrides.altText: Adds to your chance to inflict poison on hit. Each stack of poison deals poison damage over time and reduces poison resistance by 5% (2% against bosses and players).
Adds to your chance to ignite an enemy when you hit it. Ignites deals fire damage over time. An enemy can have multiple ignites at once.
Adds to your chance to chill an enemy when you hit it. Chill reduces attack speed, cast speed, and movement speed by 12%, and stacks up to 3 times.
Adds to your chance to slow an enemy when you hit it.  Slow reduces movement speed by 20% and stacks up to 3 times.

Adds to your chance to blind an enemy when you hit it. Blind causes enemies to aim erratically, reducing the chance that they will hit you, especially at range. An enemy can only have one instance of blind at a time.
Adds to your chance to cause bleeding when you hit an enemy. Bleeding deals physical damage over time. An enemy can have multiple instances of bleeding at once.
Shock reduces lightning resistance by 5%, increases chance to be stunned by 10%, lasts 4 seconds, and can stack up to 20 times. It has 60% reduced effect against bosses and players.
Each stack of Frostbite deals cold damage over time and reduces freeze avoidance, increasing the enemy's chance to be frozen.
Plague deals poison damage over time and spreads between enemies. An enemy can only have one instance of plague at a time.
Time Rot deals void damage over time, increases stun duration by 5%, lasts 3 seconds, and stacks up to 12 times.
Future Strike lasts 2 seconds then deals 60 void damage all at once at the end of its duration. Counts as damage over time.
Spark Charges are spells that explode after 0.7 seconds dealing lightning damage in an area around the target.
Adds to your chance to apply Damned to an enemy when you hit it. Damned deals necrotic damage over time and reduces health regen by 20%. An enemy can have multiple stacks of Damned at once.
Adds to your chance to apply Frailty to an enemy when you hit it.  Frailty reduces damage dealt by 6% and stacks up to 3 times.
Each stack of armour shred reduces armour by 100, increasing damage taken from all hits. Can reduce armour below 0.
Spirit Plague is a curse that deals necrotic spell damage over time for 3 seconds and spreads to other enemies when the original target dies. It cannot stack.
Doom deals massive void damage over time and increases melee damage taken by 4%. Can stack up to 4 times and each stack lasts 4 seconds.
